'''''Kanón''''' is an anime based on novel Adam Stvořitel by Karel Čapek that directed by [[Mahiro Maeda]] that was released as the 13th part of ''[[Animator Expo]]'' on {{months|3}} 13, 2015.
__TOC__
{{clear}}
== Plot ==
It's punishment.

